      "title": "Will the price of Litro decrease again?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Muditha Peiris, Chairman of Litro Gas Company, said that the price of Litro domestic gas will be reduced again from midnight on the 5th of this month and the new prices will be announced later."
